<h2>Data Source and Methodology</h2>
<p>All calculations are based on data from the Giannini Shop Online size conversion charts. For detailed standards, please refer to <a href="https://www.gianninishoponline.com/en/more-information/Size-conversion-charts/30/" target="_blank">Giannini Shop Online</a>. All calculations strictly adhere to the provided data and formulas.</p>
<h2>The Formula Explained</h2>
<div class="formula-box">
<p><strong>Conversion Formula:</strong> Size in Standard X = (Size in Standard Y * Conversion Factor)</p>
